WEBVTT

00:10.000 --> 00:12.116
-Good morning.
-Morning.

00:12.280 --> 00:13.395
Charlie, right?

00:13.560 --> 00:16.836
Well, l guess it's too late to deny it.

00:17.000 --> 00:18.718
Would you like some coffee?

00:19.680 --> 00:21.432
Sure. . .

00:23.000 --> 00:24.069
. . .l would.

00:26.120 --> 00:28.156
You have a beautiful house.

00:29.680 --> 00:31.830
Thank you. . .

00:34.880 --> 00:36.393
. . .so much.

00:37.440 --> 00:38.509
My name's Sandy.

00:39.360 --> 00:41.828
Yes, of course it is.

00:43.120 --> 00:48.797
How could l forget?
Sandy like the beach, or the Koufax.

00:49.960 --> 00:51.712
-Pardon me?
-You know, Sandy Koufax.

00:51.880 --> 00:54.314
Great Dodger pitcher,
hall-of-famer. . . . Never mind.

00:55.480 --> 00:56.913
So, Sandy. . .

00:57.080 --> 00:59.310
. . .how did you sleep?

00:59.480 --> 01:01.710
Just fine. How about you?

01:01.880 --> 01:04.792
Great. Like a drunk baby.

01:04.959 --> 01:06.393
Are you hungry?

01:06.560 --> 01:08.790
Not yet. Maybe after l throw up.

01:09.320 --> 01:10.673
What did you do last night?

01:10.840 --> 01:12.717
l was hoping you could fill me in.

01:12.880 --> 01:16.316
There's my little Sandy beach.

01:16.480 --> 01:19.278
Good morning, Alley-Oop.

01:19.680 --> 01:23.275
Oh, thank God. l was afraid
l was gonna have to quit drinking.

