15:02.760 --> 15:04.910
-Somebody's been playing with them.
-So?

15:05.080 --> 15:06.798
So l wanna know who it was.

15:07.320 --> 15:09.834
-Jake?
-l didn't do it.

15:10.000 --> 15:10.989
Charlie?

15:12.560 --> 15:16.155
Oh, all right, l may have used one
of them as a swizzle stick.

15:17.880 --> 15:19.916
Well, no harm done.

15:20.080 --> 15:22.150
lf you must play with them,
please remember. . .

15:22.320 --> 15:25.676
. . .it's Dasher, Dancer, Prancer, Vixen,
Comet, Cupid, Donner, Blitzen.

15:25.840 --> 15:26.989
Okay.

15:27.160 --> 15:29.469
Donner, Blitzen, Donner, Blitzen,
Donner, Blitzen.

15:30.880 --> 15:31.869
-Got it.
-Say it.

15:32.960 --> 15:34.518
Donner, Blitzen.

15:36.720 --> 15:38.312
Okay, then.

15:38.480 --> 15:40.948
''The Little Drummer Boy. ''

16:12.640 --> 16:15.234
Donner, Blitzen, Donner, Blitzen.

16:16.760 --> 16:19.194
Alan. Why aren't you asleep?

16:19.960 --> 16:21.188
l don't know.

16:21.360 --> 16:24.716
Just excited about Christmas, l guess.

16:25.120 --> 16:27.839
Well, Santa won't come
while you're awake.

16:28.000 --> 16:31.072
