17:52.240 --> 17:54.674
Will you listen?
There's something wrong with Sandy.

17:54.840 --> 17:57.832
Well, didn't we know that
when she agreed to sleep with you?

17:58.000 --> 18:01.959
No, no, even wronger than that.
She actually believes in Santa Claus.

18:02.120 --> 18:03.553
-Really?
-Yeah.

18:05.040 --> 18:06.519
